{"tid":689471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中方發表聲明:必須以不打貿易戰為前題下討論 否則所有經貿成果不會生效","createTime":"2018-06-04T06:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:12:05.000Z","uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de5d8cacc209105cf2916ef73bc69cada9849eba","tid":689471,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"副總理劉鶴與美國商務部長羅斯，在北京展開新一輪經貿磋商，討論中國增加購買美國產品。 中方發表聲明，警告中美之間達成的成果，前提應基於不打貿易戰，若果美方實施加徵關稅在內的貿易制裁措施，雙方談判達成的所有經貿成果將不會生效。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1399688-20180603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1399688-20180603.htm&d=kdpm3TGC%2FPzajP3Vx6HhkHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6049de53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1399688-20180603.htm&h=87df0f86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1399688-20180603.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dd2216947dd9375d4ea9998525a3bc4e17e71dbb","tid":689471,"uid":188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話唔知咩搬石頭又咩自己隻腳既"},{"pid":"948dd3308e3c2f166592ce8f806655bfd0983754","tid":689471,"uid":51932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:04:27.000Z","msg":"警告美方喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4adf6011f1bc1fbb956de02ed83d8350897006d","tid":689471,"uid":47080,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"龍門任你擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那簽完協議都無做到啦，講呢啲"},{"pid":"5729db27af9f524ee22742a3a99953ebc6e1e964","tid":689471,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.g